{"lastModified":1772463119838,"uri":"c::30042863936::vessel::fe80d490-05c8-11f1-90a8-7517306996d3","yachtType":["Motor"],"description":"Operating Area: Miami, Florida, South Beach, Biscayne Bay, Star Island, Fisher Island, Key Biscayne, Miami River, Palm Beach, Fort Lauderdale, Florida Keys\n\nThe Azimut 53 “El Faraon” is a 16.9-meter luxury motor yacht that embodies Italian elegance, performance, and innovation. Built by the renowned Azimut Yachts, this vessel delivers a perfect balance of style and comfort — ideal for both relaxing coastal cruises and longer sea adventures.\n\nDesign & Comfort\nWith sleek lines and a beautifully proportioned flybridge, El Faraon offers exceptional outdoor living. The extended flybridge includes spacious seating, sun loungers, and a retractable hardtop, creating the perfect setting for sunbathing or alfresco dining. The aft deck features a shaded dining area for outdoor meals, while the foredeck sun pads invite guests to unwind and enjoy panoramic sea views.\n\nInside, the yacht showcases modern Italian design with luxurious finishes and large windows that flood the salon with natural light. The bright main salon offers a comfortable lounge, entertainment system, and formal indoor dining area, seamlessly connected to a fully equipped galley.","blueprint":{"name":"EL FARAON","images":["/media/media::image::a::vessel::fe80d490-05c8-11f1-90a8-7517306996d3::assets::a6f437d0-05d2-11f1-9ba7-537447979a95/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::fe80d490-05c8-11f1-90a8-7517306996d3::assets::a6f57050-05d2-11f1-9ba7-537447979a95/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::fe80d490-05c8-11f1-90a8-7517306996d3::assets::a6f79330-05d2-11f1-9ba7-537447979a95/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::fe80d490-05c8-11f1-90a8-7517306996d3::assets::a6e43240-05d2-11f1-9ba7-537447979a95/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::fe80d490-05c8-11f1-90a8-7517306996d3::assets::a6e56ac0-05d2-11f1-9ba7-537447979a95/{imageVariant}",